{"tid":342690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭籌備落實兩級制利得稅及企業稅務減免 政綱:首200萬元利潤16.5%降至10%","createTime":"2017-07-31T20:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-01T07:26:21.000Z","uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b47dc16d8470a518a6d2ffcf6e34d3cf4e3bfe2d","tid":342690,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T20:58:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1620887/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%3A%E7%B1%8C%E5%82%99%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%85%A9%E7%B4%9A%E5%88%B6%E5%88%A9%E5%BE%97%E7%A8%85%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1620887%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%253A%25E7%25B1%258C%25E5%2582%2599%25E5%25BC%2595%25E5%2585%25A5%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25BE%2597%25E7%25A8%2585%25E3%2580%258D&d=T7NO%2FNCtn2YvK8aGtJMaTS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f6bbb0e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1620887/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%3A%E7%B1%8C%E5%82%99%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E3%80%8C%E5%85%A9%E7%B4%9A%E5%88%B6%E5%88%A9%E5%BE%97%E7%A8%85%E3%80%8D</a> <br />\n昨日 22:10 時事脈搏<br />\n林鄭:籌備引入「兩級制利得稅」<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥出席工業總會周年晚宴致詞時表示，現正籌備落實為鼓勵企業開發及投資而引入的稅務扣減，亦籌備引入「兩級制利得稅」，強調政府「不會走數」，會加強與工商業界的聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n她續稱，政府重視經濟發展，希望推動本港再工業化，會充分發揮促成者和推廣者的角色，盡快推進落馬洲河套地區港深創新科技園項目，以及盡快完成科技園擴建和工業邨重建，亦會透過教育為創科行業培訓人才，以不同方式吸引國際知名機構落戶香港。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，期望跟業界把握「一帶一路」及「粵港澳大灣區」所帶來的機遇；又提到香港和東盟國家的貿易發展迅速，東盟是香港第二大貿易夥伴，期望透過稍後出訪加強彼此聯繫，以及在年底前與東盟簽訂自由貿易協定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n行政長官出席香港工業總會第57屆會員周年大會晚宴致辭全文  <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201707/31/P2017073101097.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201707%2F31%2FP2017073101097.htm&d=T7NO%2FNCtn2YvK8aGtJMaTS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=d95a07b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201707/31/P2017073101097.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭：短期公布兩級制利得稅 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=230454\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D230454&d=T7NO%2FNCtn2YvK8aGtJMaTS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=e0ff3cc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D230454&h=be661fda\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=230454</a> <br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥稱籌備引入「兩級制利得稅」<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1345525-20170731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1345525-20170731.htm&d=T7NO%2FNCtn2YvK8aGtJMaTS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=03b491a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1345525-20170731.htm&h=b9ab93fd\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1345525-20170731.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9626338835bbea189afb61b5f7dbfea1cd72cde0","tid":342690,"uid":37081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T21:13:52.000Z","msg":"你老母整撚到工廈租金咁撚貴仲話推動工業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ce8ae2029b73735ec37dcbb60ff51617cafba7","tid":342690,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T07:26:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母整撚到工廈租金咁撚貴仲話推動工業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人哋話推動研發環保科技咋, 要感欣"}]}